### GET SCHOOLS
## Returns a list of schools. 
## This is usefull to find the id of the school for login.
##
## Response Body (200 OK) - Array of school objects, each containing:
##   - id            (UUID): Unique identifier of the school
##   - name          (string): Full name of the school (e.g. "Kantonsschule Agisbühl Zürich")
##   - abbreviation  (string): Short identifier (e.g. "kaz")
##   - address       (string): Address of the school
##
## Responses:
##   200 OK - Returns array of GetCourseResponse objects
##   500 Internal Server Error - Database Query failed
GET {{BASE}}/school
Accept: application/json


### CREATE A SCHOOL
## Creates a new school.
## Restricted Admin role.
##
## Request Body:
##   - name         (string, required): Full name of the school (e.g. "Kantonsschule Agisbühl Zürich")
##   - abbreviation (string, required): Short school identifier (e.g. "kaz")
##   - address      (string, required): Address of the school
##
## Responses:
##   200 OK - School created successfully; returns the new school ID
##   400 Bad Request - Missing required fields or invalid UUID format
##   401 Unauthorized - Insufficient permissions for this role
##   403 Forbidden - No active session
##   500 Internal Server Error - Database Query failed
##
## @name ksh
POST {{BASE}}/school
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json


{
    "name": "Kantonsschule Hottingen",
    "abbreviation": "ksh",
    "address": "Minervastrasse 14, 8090 Zürich"
}